David Bulman, 55, and his wife Lubova had a row after he criticised her for not doing the ironing .
His wife threw all his shirts outside but he followed her and pulled her hair .
Neighbours called the police after Bulman drove away, damaging a gate post and a van .
Bulman was given a 12-month community order after he pleaded guilty to assault occasioning actual bodily harm at Bristol Crown Court .